    "version": "MCNP6.3.0 (ld=01/26/23, release/6.3-55762725c4)",
    "notes": "Results contributed by Hrvoje Brkic. F4 tally = track-length flux; F6 tally = dose. DLET/TLET/DQEFF/TQEFF (native medium) derived from LET spectra via ICRP-60 Q(L) weighting. DOSE/DLET/TLET .H2O depth variants and DLET/TLET .H2O target variants derived via Bragg-Gray water-equivalent conversion (protons/primary only). Depth DQEFF/TQEFF .H2O are also produced but not yet declared in output_catalog.json (see raw_output block below)."
  },
  "provenance": {
    "date": null,
